## Packer Template Design

### File Structure
```
packer/
├── tatin.pkr.hcl          # Main Packer template
├── variables.pkr.hcl      # Variable definitions
└── scripts/
    ├── base-system.sh     # Core packages
    ├── python.sh          # Python 3 setup
    ├── golang.sh          # Go 1.23.5 setup
    ├── bun.sh             # Bun runtime
    ├── nodejs.sh          # Node.js LTS
    ├── claude-code.sh     # Claude Code CLI
    ├── opencode.sh        # OpenCode CLI
    ├── crush.sh           # Crush agent
    └── finalize.sh        # Final cleanup
```

### Packer Template (tatin.pkr.hcl)
```hcl
packer {
  required_plugins {
    tart = {
      version = ">= 1.12.0"
      source  = "github.com/cirruslabs/tart"
    }
  }
}

source "tart-cli" "tatin" {
  from_oci       = "ghcr.io/cirruslabs/debian:latest"
  vm_name        = "tatin"
  cpu_count      = 4
  memory_gb      = 8
  disk_size_gb   = 20
  ssh_username   = "admin"
  ssh_password   = "admin"
  ssh_timeout    = "120s"
}

build {
  sources = ["source.tart-cli.tatin"]

  # Base system
  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/base-system.sh"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  # Language runtimes (sequential - some depend on others)
  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/python.sh"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/golang.sh"
  }

  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/nodejs.sh"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/bun.sh"
    execute_command = "chmod +x {{ .Path }}; {{ .Vars }} sudo -E -u admin bash '{{ .Path }}'"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  # Agent tools (unprivileged)
  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/claude-code.sh"
    execute_command = "chmod +x {{ .Path }}; {{ .Vars }} sudo -E -u admin bash '{{ .Path }}'"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/opencode.sh"
    execute_command = "chmod +x {{ .Path }}; {{ .Vars }} sudo -E -u admin bash '{{ .Path }}'"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/crush.sh"
    execute_command = "chmod +x {{ .Path }}; {{ .Vars }} sudo -E -u admin bash '{{ .Path }}'"
    environment_vars = ["DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive"]
  }

  # Cleanup and finalize
  provisioner "shell" {
    script = "scripts/finalize.sh"
  }

  post-processor "manifest" {
    output = "manifest.json"
  }
}
```

### Key Design Decisions

1. **Tart Plugin**: Use cirruslabs/tart plugin v1.12+ for native Tart integration
2. **OCI Base Image**: Pull from ghcr.io/cirruslabs/debian:latest (same as Vagrantfile)
3. **Modular Scripts**: Each provisioner as separate .sh file for maintainability
4. **Privilege Handling**: Root for system packages, admin user for user-space tools
5. **SSH Auth**: Use existing admin/admin credentials from base image

### Variables (variables.pkr.hcl)
```hcl
variable "go_version" {
  type    = string
  default = "1.23.5"
}

variable "vm_name" {
  type    = string
  default = "tatin"
}

variable "cpu_count" {
  type    = number
  default = 4
}

variable "memory_gb" {
  type    = number
  default = 8
}

variable "disk_size_gb" {
  type    = number
  default = 20
}
```

### Build Commands
```bash
# Initialize plugins
packer init packer/

# Validate template
packer validate packer/

# Build image
packer build packer/

# Build with custom variables
packer build -var 'vm_name=tatin-dev' -var 'cpu_count=8' packer/
```

### Registry Publishing (optional)
```bash
# Push to ghcr.io
tart push tatin ghcr.io/$ORG/tatin:latest

# Use in Vagrant
tart.image = "ghcr.io/$ORG/tatin:latest"
```
